article.description: — Sincere Carry had 20 points as Kent State topped George Washington 77-69 on Tuesday.
article.headline: Carry lifts Kent State over George Washington 77-69
article.linkText: Carry lifts Kent State over George Washington 77-69
article.story: NAPLES, Fla. -- — Sincere Carry had 20 points as Kent State topped George Washington 77-69 on Tuesday. Carry made 4 of 6 3-pointers. Giovanni Santiago had 12 points for Kent State (3-1). Malique Jacobs also scored 12 points with seven rebounds and seven assists. Tervell Beck had 10 points. James Bishop had 19 points for the Colonials (2-5). Joe Bamisile added 15 points and Brayon Freeman had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
